public static class NosqlDbFactory.CloudSimProvider extends Object implements oracle.nosql.driver.AuthorizationProvider
A simple provider that uses a manufactured id for use by the Cloud Simulator. It is used as a namespace for tables and not for any actual authorization or authentication.
